The conversation includes a shared link to the "GM.AI Airdrop Portal" with a message about joining the $GM Airdrop. The chat continues with messages in Vietnamese discussing various topics, including a story update, losing some items, and a mention of "Dogs major." The timestamps indicate the conversation took place on August 3rd and the following day. The chat background features a light green color with playful doodles.

flow_desc: In this user flow, the request is to initiate a call. The interaction begins in a Telegram chat with a contact named "Hao," where a shared link to the "GM.AI Airdrop Portal" is discussed, along with messages about various topics, including personal updates and a mention of "Dogs major." The conversation spans over two days in Vietnamese, conveyed against a playful light green background. To fulfill the request, the user will tap on the phone icon within the chat interface, triggering the phone call to "Hao," thus connecting them directly for further discussions.
